 247:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h **** /* Determine whether or not stack checking is enabled. By default, ThreadX stack checking is
 248:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    disabled. When the following is defined, ThreadX thread stack checking is enabled.  If stack
 249:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    checking is enabled (TX_ENABLE_STACK_CHECKING is defined), the TX_DISABLE_STACK_FILLING
 250:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    define is negated, thereby forcing the stack fill which is necessary for the stack checking
 251:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    logic.  */
 252:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h **** 
